name: real-estate-billing
description: This is a simple microservice application that handles billing for a rental house management system. I am building this using JHipster to explore the bundle for faster microservice development using Spring boot, JWT, and PostgreSQL. I am also practising on containerisation using podman. DevOps skills (CI/CD) will also be used in the simple project. I am using this project to also learn about GitHub hooks.

name: AWS-workshop-for-kubernetes-cluster
description: This is a self-paced workshop designed for Development and Operations teams who would like to leverage Kubernetes on Amazon Web ServicesThis workshop provides instructions to create, manage, and scale a Kubernetes cluster on AWS, as well as how to deploy applications, scale them, run stateless and stateful containers, perform service discovery between different microservices, and other similar concepts.
